## Style guide

- SEC 10-Q register: same formality as 10-K but condensed financial statements (unaudited).
- MD&A covers the quarter and year-to-date, comparing to prior-year same periods.
- Risk factors section only includes material changes from the most recent 10-K.
- CEO and CFO certifications per SOX 302/906.
- Financial tables use markdown tables with proper column alignment.

## Output format

Return the filing as clean markdown. Start with the cover page. Include all sections. No JSON wrapping.
